            <h3>Wake Forest Food Truck Alley Website</h3>
            <p>The Wake Forest Food Truck Alley (WFFTA) was a website that I created for a National Contest held by the Future Business Leaders of America Association. The website won second place at the National Leadership Convention in Atlanta, GA during June of 2023.</p>
