            <h3>JoyFuse Stem Kits for Kids Website</h3>
            <p>JoyFuse Stem Kits for Kids is a company that creates STEM kits geared towards children ages 5-13. I partnered with them to create an engaging online platform that promotes their products and resources for STEM education.</p>
