            <p>Beyond the Blazer is an NC FBLA-Collegiate Podcast that is hosted by Jeremy Post, VP of Membership for North Carolina FBLA-Collegiate. I am the editor and graphic designer for the podcast. Check out Beyond the Blazer on Spotify, Apple Podcast, or Youtube.</p>
